	ago. In the future, hundreds of billions of smart sensors and devices
	will interact with one another without human intervention, on a Machine-to-Machine
	(M2M) basis. They will generate an enormous amount of data at an
	unprecedented scale and resolution, providing humans with information
	and control of events and objects even in remote physical environments.
